{"text_id":38679,"tokens":["Evaluating"," conjun","ctive"," queries"," and"," solving"," constraint"," satisfaction"," problems"," are"," fundamental"," problems"," in"," database"," theory"," and"," artificial"," intelligence",","," respectively","."," These"," problems"," are"," NP","-","hard",","," so"," that"," several"," research"," efforts"," have"," been"," made"," to"," find"," a"," solution"," for"," them","."," The"," approach"," proposed"," here"," is"," based"," on"," the"," notion"," of"," a"," solver"," and"," takes"," advantage"," of"," the"," fact"," that"," the"," search"," problem"," can"," be"," decomposed"," into"," two"," distinct"," parts",":"," a"," tra","ctable"," part"," (","the"," first"," kind",")"," and"," an"," intractable"," one"," (","second"," kind",")."," By"," using"," this"," approach",","," it"," is"," possible"," to"," develop"," a"," robust"," and"," efficient"," algorithm"," for"," dynamically"," combining"," these"," two"," types"," of"," problems"," within"," a"," single"," computer"," execution","."," We"," propose"," a"," multi","-","element"," framework"," for"," interrelated"," programming"," languages"," (","MIP","Ls","),"," where"," each"," language"," can"," independently"," implement"," various"," components"," of"," its"," own"," program"," model"," without"," having"," to"," resort"," to"," shared"," code","."," MIP","Ls"," provide"," a"," flexible"," means"," to"," express"," abstract"," programmers","'"," ideas"," as"," concrete"," programs","."," In"," particular",","," we"," introduce"," the"," concept"," of"," encapsulated"," modules",","," which"," we"," define"," as"," module"," implementations"," of"," M","IPL"," concepts"," designed"," with"," concurrency"," in"," mind","."," We"," then"," describe"," how"," embedded"," classes",","," which"," are"," used"," by"," many"," MIP","Ls"," today",","," can"," be"," quickly"," converted"," from"," pure"," abstraction"," models"," into"," modular"," implementations